doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Company Profile Verification Update
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .reason {
        background-color: #fff5f5;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
  body
    .container
      .header
        h1 ⚠️ Company Profile Verification Update
      p Hello #{userName},
      p We have reviewed your company profile for "#{companyName}" and unfortunately, we were unable to verify it at this time.
      .reason
        p
          strong Reason:
        p #{rejectionMessage}
      p
        strong What you can do:
      ul
        li Review the feedback provided above
        li Update your company profile with the necessary corrections
        li Resubmit your profile for verification
      p Once you've made the required changes, please log in to your account and update your company profile. Our team will review it again promptly.
      p If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
      p Thank you for your understanding.
